text: Jodie Dobson (born 5 September 1960) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
